JOHANNESBURG –Exclusive Books said on Tuesday they would be offering a refund for “dissatisfied” customers who purchased Bonang Matheba's book, Bonang: From A to B. This follows heavy social media backlash on the book after readers noticed and posted pictures of several spelling mistakes and grammatical errors. READ: Euphonik takes a dig at Bonang's book with 'drugs, lies' comments The satement read," Exclusive Books wishes to extend its apologies to any customers who were disatiefied with thier purchase." eNCA